      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While the engine starts and the car is drivable, it shows visible signs of age including some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor dents on the passenger side. The interior has some wear on the upholstery and the air conditioning requires a recharge. This would be an excellent choice for someone looking for a reliable commuter who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections or a bit of weekend DIY work to bring it back to its best.",
