    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. I've taken really good care of it, and it\u2019s ready for many more adventures with its next owner. It runs beautifully and is just waiting for someone to take it home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
