    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings were recently serviced. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, offering the communicative feedback and balanced handling characteristic of the M-division's peak era. While the exterior shows minor road wear, the drivetrain is dialed in for immediate performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
