    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The VarioCam Plus system ensures a broad powerband, while the chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. Critical preventative maintenance is addressed with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recent rear main seal replacement. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors for exceptional thermal management and pedal feel. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp and uncompromised.",
